Dr.Chitra .J.A.
She was a lovely person . She care a lot very humble and friendly nature.her interaction with persons feels like half disses reduces.
She is patient and empathetic towards what the patient has to say. She made me feel very comfortable.

The doctor Chithra was very humble and calm..... She treated with care and the Can Well clinic is also gud... It's with clean, neat and positive environment..... Yes I would recommend this clinic and doctor to my friends and relatives .
I gone for my daughter's treatment. Doctor made a observation and gave counseling and created well. The clinic also have nice ambience.

Dr.Ramaprabha has a special skill of putting fwd things in a very positive tone, which makes us comfortable... Kudos to Dr for that attitude.., I would prefer to refer Dr. Ramaprabha for any pregnant women for safe delivery...!!! Hats-off to her experience.
